        Work
    </h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>🟢 I'm available and actively looking for work! Please <a href="mailto:emiliawilliamson@pm.me">get in touch</a> if you have a role that might be a good fit.</strong></li>
        <li>My time at The Economist came to an end in May 2026 during a round of layoffs. I'm very happy to be keeping in touch with a lot of my former colleagues though, and forcing them to look at pictures of my vegetable trug.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Personal</h2>
    <p>
        <ul>
            <li>I've been focussing on being a well-rounded person, trying to take care of my health, see friends and family, read a lot, contribute to my community, and learn new things.</li>
            <li>At the end of last year I bought my first house, a cosy little place on the outskirts of Stoke-on-Trent. For all the bad rap the city gets, my partner and I have been loving it. Having the Peaks on our doorstep, a cosy little board game cafe in town, and tons of greeen spaces to take the dog has been a real treat.</li>
